a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">379</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:857\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">857</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg001.perseus-grc1:943\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ach.\">Ach.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">943</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.). b. c. opt. in orat. obliq., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:5:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HG\">HG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.5.23</biblScope> </bibl>; after opt. in principal clause, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Oec.\">Oec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.13</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n116421.10\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> with <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ subj.\">subj.</a></mood>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in order that,</tr_> in Thessalian dialect, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸς ταμίας φροντίσαι οὕστε . . γενειθεῖ τᾶ πόλι ἁ δόσις</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ BCH\">BCH</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">59.38</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<placeName TEIform=\"place